abstracts.cdata!:
This project consists of: i) the
            rehabilitation of the northern half (160 km) of the
            Parakou-Malanville route; ii) the rehabilitation of the
            southern half (160 km) of the Parakou-Malanville route and
            of two sections (20 km) of the Cotonou-Bohicon road; iii)
            supervision by consultants of the rehabilitation mentioned
            in items (i) and (ii); and iv) extension of the existing
            highway maintenance program by providing additional
            technical assistance and materials.
